2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper proposes a deep transfer learning method, which is a popular technique in machine learning. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper addresses a problem that is relevant to artificial intelligence, specifically in the area of image recognition. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The paper uses deep learning techniques, which are a subset of neural computing. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with image recognition, which is a common application in multimedia.
